                  <decoDesc ana="low">
                     <decoNote type="initial">
                        <p>Traces of colored initials according to Kålund (Kat. I:739).</p>
                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" subtype="marginal">Small figure drawn in the lower margin of fol.
                        <locus>14v</locus>. Grotesque figure in lower 
                        margin of fol. <locus>67r</locus>.</decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  
                  <additions ana="low">
                     <p>Occasional marginalia and pen tests throughout.</p> 
                        <p>Autograph of a certain <q>Olaf</q> in the lower margins of fols. 
                        <locus>25r</locus>, <locus>27r</locus> and <locus from="28v" to="28v">28v</locus>. Other autographs by
                        <name type="person">Snjófríður</name>, fol <locus from="75v" to="75v">75v</locus> and <name type="person">Sigmundur
                           Hallsson</name>, fol. <locus from="76r" to="76r">76r</locus>.</p>
                        <p>Inserted page in the hand of <name type="person" role="owner" key="ArnMag001">AM</name> reads: 
                        <q>afftan af sögu Eigils einhendta
                           vilihalms siods saga. 
                           saga af Bosa <ex>og</ex> Herraudi. 
                           af Þorsteini Bæiarmagn fragm<ex>en</ex>t. 
                           af Vilmundi vidutan. fragm<ex>en</ex>t. 
                           af Flores k<ex>on</ex>gi <ex>og</ex> sonu<ex>m</ex> h<ex>an</ex>s 
                           <del type="overstrike">(ut puto)</del> fragment. 
                           (Pall skrifar þ<ex>ar</ex> se i af Bratleifi <add place="below">bondasyni nockrum</add> 
                           <add place="below">Þetta Bratleifs nafn er oriett, komid af rangre lesningu</add>
                           nockru<ex>m</ex> fragment.</q> Facing page has inscription addressed to: <q>Monsr Arne a Kiöbenhaffn</q>.
                     </p>
                  </additions>
                  
